{"tid":2347422,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"特朗普團隊入稟最高法院尋求推翻威州選舉結果","createTime":"2020-12-31T04:42:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-31T05:35:58.000Z","uid":362414,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a49ea2f94c17e56b0d79b0f8f2446072eecf94e2","tid":2347422,"uid":362414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T04:42:32.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普的競選團隊入稟美國最高法院，尋求推翻當選人拜登在威斯康星州勝選的結果。<br />\n<br />\n早前聯邦法院和巡迴上訴法院已經先後拒絕要求。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，美國國會1月6日將計算各州選舉人票，作為正式確認大選結果的最後程序。<br />\n<br />\n共和黨籍參議員霍利宣布將挑戰有關程序。較早前，有共和黨籍眾議員透露計劃挑戰認證程序。<br />\n<br />\n美國法律規定，要挑戰州的選舉人票，至少要由一位眾議員及一位參議員提出，屆時國會認證程序將暫停，兩院將分別進行時間不超過2小時辯論，之後分別進行表決，決定是否接納。<br />\n<br />\n但目前眾議院民主黨佔優，而參議院包括共和黨領袖麥康奈爾曾公開反對作出挑戰，意味要成功挑戰機會好微。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1568006-20201231.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1568006-20201231.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=BLGvZshAgiFYydKSMDjJm6zbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=f4b0b58c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1568006-20201231.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=0a7b15aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1568006-20201231.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"70acd1d5d0748a3d0e3261b2f39ce4b6248b4a40","tid":2347422,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T04:44:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89c404ecd6e8a35d686d11279b945b48bbeda988","tid":2347422,"uid":31215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T04:53:52.000Z","msg":"意味要成功挑戰機會好微<br />\n意味要成功挑戰機會好微<br />\n意味要成功挑戰機會好微<br />\n意味要成功挑戰機會好微<br />\n<br />\n冇啦其實"}